snippet.title: Target Party Gameplay July 2023
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2467370/Target_Party/

Target Party is a first-person platform game that will make you feel the adrenaline of speed and the art of speedrunning. You have only one goal: destroy all the targets before you reach the finish line.
Will you be the fastest?
